        <mxCell id="dfText" value="SSR: getProps → ssrBffGet('/products/:sku') → { product } → SSRProductProvider&#xa;Client: PdpProvider → useProduct(sku) → useSSRProduct().product as initialData → usePDP().product&#xa;BuyBox: usePDP().product → GiftCardBuyBox renders form fields based on product.c_gcType&#xa;Amount: useGiftCardLocation syncs ?amount= param ↔ usePDP().giftCardAmount ↔ ChipList selection" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
